Application.Domain

Class QueryWord

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.QueryWord

  • @Entity
public class QueryWord
extends java.lang.Object
    QueryWord is the class that maps the database Entity QueryWord. A QueryWord is a word for which a User searched for while creating the Picture of a Vision.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
